sourcesContent: import {MDBBtn,MDBTableBody} from "mdb-react-ui-kit"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import Filter from "./Filter"; const Task = (props) => { const todos = useSelector((state) => state.todos); const dispatch=useDispatch const finishsubmit=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault() dispatch(finshtodo) } return ( <> 1 Buy groceries for next week In progress Delete Finished Edit 2 Renew car insurance In progress Delete Finished 3 Sign up for online course In progress Delete Finished ); } export default Task;
